Static init

  • init(bootstrapModule: any, rootPath?: string, moduleMetaKey?: string, authProvider?: AuthProvider, container?: Container): HttpServer
    • Defined in classes/http-server.class.ts:67

    Initialize the application by creating new httpServer.

    A bootstrap module (boostrapModule) should be decorated with SugModule and 'modules' property which contains all of the related modules. Depended on moduleMetaKey for separate applications.

    Parameters

    • bootstrapModule: any

      the root module which use as entry point

    • Default value rootPath: string = "/"

      the prefix for all of the routes

    • Default value moduleMetaKey: string = ModuleMetaKey

      related to SugModule metaKey

    • Default value authProvider: AuthProvider = null

      -

    • Default value container: Container = new Container()

      the inversify Container which will be use to for binding the services

    Returns HttpServer
